Install dependencies
=============================

We suggest running in a virtualenv::

  python setup.py develop 


How to run
=============================

Show bot options::

  python icvbot.py --help


Example bot usage::

  python icvbot.py --server=irc.freenode.net --channel=#icv


Plugins
=============================

plugins must be structured in this way::

  #!/usr/bin/python
  def main(*argv):
      <<<code>>>
      return string
      or return string logstring
      or return [string1,string2,...]
      or return [string1,string2,...] logstring


